  <summary>1/22/2015--Introduced.
Protecting Life in Funding Education Act or the PRO-LIFE Act

Amends the General Education Provisions Act to prohibit the provision of federal education funding to state or local educational agencies that make health services available to students through school-based health centers, unless those centers certify that they will not provide students with abortions, abortion-related materials or referrals, or directions to abortion services.</summary>
